Introduction

Jamie (formerly known as Jimin Park) is a South Korean singer-songwriter and TV host currently under Plan B Entertainment. She was one half of the duo 15&.
She made her solo debut on April 5, 2015 with the single "Hopeless Love".

On August 5, it was announced by JYP Entertainment that after discussion with her, the decision was made to not renew her contract. Her final release with the agency titled "Stay Beautiful" was released on August 26.

On April 20, she announced on her Twitter account that she was changing her stage name to Jamie and that she had signed with Warner Music Korea.
